position to be

00:56:00.060 --> 00:56:03.900 align:middle line:84%
an influencer of the child
at a phase of his or her life

00:56:03.900 --> 00:56:06.220 align:middle line:84%
when he can't really go to
mom and dad as comfortably,

00:56:06.220 --> 00:56:08.320 align:middle line:84%
but might be able to
go to a grandparent

00:56:08.320 --> 00:56:11.260 align:middle line:84%
if the grandparent really
has the feeling of safety.

00:56:11.260 --> 00:56:11.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Safe.

00:56:11.940 --> 00:56:13.660 align:middle line:90%
That's a very important role.

